flask project structure
    -----website folder  
        ----static folder
        ----templates folder
        ----__init__.py
        ----models.py
        ----views.py
    ----main.py

step 1 : initialize  and create the app in a function
        and mention the secret key  in __init__.py

step 2: importing the function created in above step into main.py and fethcing the app created
        and running the app

step 3: set the routes of webpages in views.py

step 4 : import the views(blueprint) into the __init__.py and register the blueprint in    the      __init__.py


